title: -TRASH-
body:
a/n - i wanted to write this for myself so i’m sorryyy.

words count - 1373

pairings -  pyro x reader

warnings - idk break ups and sadness? fluffy towards the end

—

“hey pyro let’s leave now come on,” you and some others from the reddit crew were currently at henry’s. your boyfriend niall, or youtuber pyrocynical, was a bit tipsy and it was getting late so you wanted to go back to his.

“not now y/n,” he replied, but it was in a pissed off tone. 

“pleassseeee,” 

“y/n no just fucking leave by yourself if you want to,” you were taken back. he was only doing this because he was drunk, right?

“w-what?” niall usually wasn’t like this, and he never swore at you, never. by now most of the laughter from the others had died down, listening to the conversation between you and your boyfriend.

“you fucking heard me y/n. just leave and go home, you know what go back to alex’s and george’s, don’t go to mine. just leave me alone, im fucking sick of you being so selfish all the time, just go away!” 

and so you did. you picked up your purse off of the coffee table and walked out of henry’s flat. tears started falling down onto your cheeks and you couldn’t be bothered to wipe them away.

you unlocked you car and got in, starting the engine. once again, you did what niall told you to do and drove to your own flat which you shared with the youtubers imallexx and memeulous. you lived in the flat, but you were hardly ever there, you were always at nialls. shit. all my stuff is at his.

once you made your way to your shared flat, your parked you car on the street outside. you raced up to the flat and loudly knocked on the door, tears spilling from your eyes. 

the door opened and you were met with george, immediately falling into his arms.

1 week later

you hadn’t seen and let alone talked to niall for a week despite getting many missed calls and texts from him. you just ignored them. you were back to living with two of your best friends. of course you told them everything that had happened.

but all your belongings were still at nialls, and you had to go get it. it was early in the morning, around 7. not wanting to wake your room mates up you tiptoed down the hallway and out the front door.

time skipppppp

you had finally arrived at nialls, after about a 30 minute drive. tears were threatening to fall from your eyes again but you quickly blinked and you were back to normal. 

you walked up to his flat and knocked on the door loudly, hoping you would wake him as he would probably be asleep. you heard footsteps and the door opened wide. you just stared at him. his eyes were swollen and puffy, a dead give away that had been crying.

“y/n?” he said in a whisper. you couldn’t take it so you walked passed him and up into your once shared room. you started crying, you couldn’t help it, letting out many loud sobs.

you got all your clothes and dumped them into a garbage bag which you had brought. you felt arms wrap around your waist but you wiggled out of nialls grasp and stared him in the eyes, crying as hard as ever.

“niall i’m sorry but no, i can’t do it, not again,” and with that you walked out of the room and out of the flat.

once you got back to your car, you got into the drivers seat and dumped your clothes in the back. you started the car with a shaky hand. 

3 weeks later

you and niall had broken up a month ago. within that month you had been inactive on all social media, including youtube. you were a youtuber with 2 and a half million subscribers.

you felt like you had to tell your viewers why you were so inactive so you sat in the chair by your desk which you recorded in and turned on the camera. 

“uh hey guys, long time no see?” you took in a deep breathe trying to think about what you were going to say next.

“i’m probably not going to edit this video because i really can’t be fucked so i apologise in advance for any excessive swearing, stuttering and crying. uh this past month has been very fucking hard for me. there are several reasons but as you guys can tell i’m back living with george and alex, and we got evicted so we’re in a new place, so that’s been shitty. we are all struggling trying to get comfortable with this new flat.” and then tears started spilling from your eyes, rolling down your cheeks. you used the sleeve of your hoodie, which just so happened to be nialls, and wiped them away. 

“but that’s not all. umm. okay, so i had been dating someone for 8 months, i’m not going to name them because i respect their privacy. we broke up a month ago, and if you guys cant for some reason tell, i’ve been having a hard time cooperating with that. please don’t give me empathy, it is partially my fault that things didn’t end too well, but also please don’t ask me about it guys. thank you guys for still supporting me, i’m not sure when i’m going to be recording again. it could be tomorrow, next week, in a month, even a year. but uh yeah… thank you,” and with that you turned off that camera and started publishing it to your channel. 

1 month later

it was around mid-day. you told the boys that you were heading out to starbucks, the starbucks that you and niall always use to go to. 

you ordered the usual. a tall vanilla frappuccino, one shot of coffee and of course whipped cream. once you got the drink you sat down in a booth next to the window.

you unlocked your phone and scrolled through twitter, sipping on your drink. you decided to search up pyrcocynical. suspended, what a surprise. 

you two had broken up 2 months ago, and the last time you talked was around the same time. you heard the door to the cafe open but didn’t look up from your phone, however you raised your eyebrow slightly when you heard a familiar voice. 

“uh hi, can i please get a small hot chocolate,” 

“name?”

“niall,”

at that your head shot upwards and saw a tall blonde man, starring at his phone while waiting for his hot chocolate. he was wearing a hoodie which had the pyrocynical logo on the back, typical him. while you continued to stare you saw  a few teenagers approaching you. 

“omg y/t/n!! i can’t believe it’s you,” at your channel name niall turned around and met your own eyes, your jaw dropped a little. you were snapped out of your trance when you heard the teenagers asking if they could get a photo, of course you said yes.

once that little encounter ended you looked back up at niall, who now had his hot chocolate, and found him still starring at you. you gestured him to come to you, so he did. 

he sat down opposite to you, the silence was almost comforting.

“so uh, how have you been?” he finally asked.

“good, how about you?” you replied, a sadness in your voice.

“yeah same to be honest,” his head fell down and he was looking at his lap, fiddling with the hot chocolate.

“we’re both lying aye,” at that he looked up at you and nodded his head lightly.

“god i’ve missed you so much y/n,”

“same naill, and i’m so fucking sorry for what i did at yours i shou-” you stared but you were cut off.

“no y/n don’t you dare apologise, i’m sorry, i should’ve said jack shit that night. all you wanted to do was to support me but i pushed you away,” he said in between a few sniffs and voice cracks.

“i- i never stopped loving you pyro,” you swear at that his eyes glistened with hope.

“same y/n- fuck it i still love you so much, be mine again? we can start from the beginning?”

“niall, i never fucking stopped being yours,”
